{"tid":652311,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同自己伴侶相處得好攰","createTime":"2018-05-03T18:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T10:32:09.000Z","uid":141495,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ed1649cb215e15bf50a9210eb5cc4fa9fdcf7a","tid":652311,"uid":141495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"有無巴/絲打 有經驗分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴身既巴/絲打，點同非痴身伴侶相處？<br />\n<br />\n我自己係個痴身男，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然女朋友無話特別討厭我痴身，<br />\n但係我自己都有收斂、抑制下行為，<br />\n目的都係唔想佢覺得有壓力。<br />\n<br />\n重點嚟了，究竟伴侶點樣做到完全唔痴身？<br />\n簡直就好似唔需要我咁，<br />\n令我無時無刻，都懷疑自己既價值地位。<br />\n好多時候只有我搵佢，<br />\n佢唔會主動想搵我。<br />\n但係佢有表明好愛我，所以我相信佢，。<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好攰，往往都係我不斷地付出，<br />\n我不斷付出愛與關懷比佢，<br />\n那我呢？點解我會感覺唔到愛，<br />\n我只感覺到寂寞同空虛，<br />\n感覺只有自己一個人<br />\n陪著你一起，但有著距離！<br />\n<br />\n種感覺有無人明白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發泄完畢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d4847a964ac927a2aca6c12930b3b12b160aa0","tid":652311,"uid":21729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"我明呀"},{"pid":"c85bde3eaa50d6b9c2c3afbe5362fc56bfbde8ff","tid":652311,"uid":141495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d4847a964ac927a2aca6c12930b3b12b160aa0","tid":652311,"uid":21729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"我明呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T18:20:29.000Z","msg":"巴打你都係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以分享下喎<img src=\"/assets/fac